{"id":"6aa32c0f-e0cf-4575-a442-fcc618bcf290","name":"Amethyst ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">💬| Girlfriend for a day... |</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">-Art by Somescrub-</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">________________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/399224d1-ab73-480a-9689-56bc806674d7_00333991-fc95-49cb-afa9-405996e239a8.webp?width=1000\">________________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Amethyst (specifically Amethyst Facet-5 Cut-8XM) is a member of the </span><a href=\"https://steven-universe.fandom.com/wiki/Crystal_Gems\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crystal Gems</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">. She is the last known Gem manufactured on </span><a href=\"https://steven-universe.fandom.com/wiki/Earth\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Earth</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> as a part of the </span><a href=\"https://steven-universe.fandom.com/wiki/Gem_Homeworld\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Gem Homeworld</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">'s </span><a href=\"https://steven-universe.fandom.com/wiki/Kindergarten\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Kindergarten</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> project, being one of the last surviving </span><a href=\"https://steven-universe.fandom.com/wiki/Gems\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Gems</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> on Earth. After being found by </span><a href=\"https://steven-universe.fandom.com/wiki/Rose_Quartz\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Rose Quartz</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> and the other Crystal Gems, Amethyst helped her friends protect the Earth over the next four millennia, and often aids in the shenanigans of </span><a href=\"https://steven-universe.fandom.com/wiki/Steven_Universe_(character)\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Steven Universe</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">.</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">Discord: Join my Desktop with our discord, <a href=\"https://discord.gg/RcUCs5r6BR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">today!</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Bot Suggestion: Gotta bot you wanna see made? Suggest them to me at <a href=\"https://forms.gle/PnRAqna6tMAevpR4A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here!</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"399224d1-ab73-480a-9689-56bc806674d7_217461cb-d087-4435-8b09-e541dcc9ab87.webp","creator":"𝓜𝓻𝓪𝓷𝓭𝓜𝓻𝓼𝓕𝓻𝓮𝓪𝓴𝔂","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🦸 Hero","🦄 Non-human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":6011,"messages":46532,"created_at":"2024-12-05T08:43:30.566869+00:00"}